{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ad061adc1","title":"陈伯达与韩爱晶蒯大富的谈话","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bd81608b5d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":8,"articleId":"0ad061adc1"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2f4604811e","type":"title","text":"陈伯达与韩爱晶蒯大富的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"f92898670c","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"b5e5497fe1","type":"paragraph","text":"八日晚到九日凌晨，敬爱的陈伯达同志、谢富治副总理等接见了韩爱晶、蒯大富等同志，陈伯达同志和他们进行了亲切的谈话。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"62fa18befa","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：现在存在的问题是不深入地探讨问题，对周围的事没有很好地考虑，心总在飞(指总想外流)。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"21fdcac058","type":"paragraph","text":"韩爱晶：(大意)聂元梓、蒯大富、韩爱晶……我们这几个人是小资产阶级，都快成修正主义了，要求到外地火线上去锻炼。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"48b2d0c682","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：你们的毛病很多，你们还不是修正主义，你们要接近群众，学习主席著作，要有群众感情。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"4db8b1ac70","type":"paragraph","text":"蒯大富：我们这几个人风头太多。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"23cc04752d","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达：你们风头是出了不少，风头主义是腐蚀人啊！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"9c65354e43","type":"paragraph","text":"(韩爱晶同志又谈了要防止产生修正主义)","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"c967793006","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志写了：战斗，学习！战斗，学习！战斗，学习！","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"},{"id":"cd9e2aafab","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，陈伯达同志乘车送韩、蒯至北航、清华并意味深长的说：无限的希望，无限的光明、无限的前途，行百里者半九十，你们还只走了半里啊！","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1"}],"page":{"id":"6bfd50bfb8","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0ad061adc1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}